    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2011 BMW M3 (E92) in pristine condition. This example features the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, utilizing individual throttle bodies to reach an 8,400 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. This ZCP-equipped unit includes the Competition Package's 10mm lowered suspension, remapped Electronic Damper Control (EDC), and 19-inch Style 359M forged wheels. Mechanically impeccable, it has undergone preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The chassis remains rigid with zero subframe issues, offering a pure, analog driving experience in a turn-key package.",
